==相关事件==
2006年11月29日，三名窃贼从熙公祠门柱上的“麻雀戏梅”和“双凤朝牡丹”石雕各一块撬下盗走，后将石雕运至[[饶平县|饶平县]][[新丰镇|新丰镇]]，并以11000[[人民币|人民币]]价格的贱卖<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 南方网 | title = 千斤顶盗国宝石雕　从熙公祠文物被盗案告破 | url = http://www.southcn.com/news/gdnews/nanyuetuijian/200701160234.htm | author = 付昱 | date = 2007-01-16 | accessdate = 2009-06-30 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304221205/http://www.southcn.com/news/gdnews/nanyuetuijian/200701160234.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2007年1月9日，案件破获<ref name="criminals">{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 南方网（转自广州日报） | title = 被盗近四十天 “国宝”石雕今回家 | url = http://www.southcn.com/news/dishi/chaozhou/ttxw/200701160070.htm | author = 阮晓光、陈正新、王冲寒 | date = 2007-01-16 | accessdate = 2009-06-30 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304200307/http://www.southcn.com/news/dishi/chaozhou/ttxw/200701160070.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，后潮安县人民法院开庭审理判决，分别判处三名罪犯有期徒刑13年、11年和10年<ref name="oh">{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 网易（转自南方网） | title = 从熙公祠石雕盗案宣判　3罪犯一审分别被判10至13年徒刑 | url = http://news.163.com/07/0918/17/3OMIOPPV000120GU.html | author = 余映涛 | date = 2007-09-18 | accessdate =  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190222112419/http://news.163.com/07/0918/17/3OMIOPPV000120GU.html | archive-date = 2019-02-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

2007年1月15日，两块石雕重新回到从熙公祠<ref name="criminals" />。

